venue.name: Nutts Pond - Precourt Park - Off of South Willow

item.description: I was there today and the park is hardly used. It is mostly fenced in and the snow is not beaten down except on the sides. I'd love to meet earlier but realize that most people work during the day. Bring your headlamps and your dogs!
item.how_to_find_us: Fenced yard right off So. Willow. Look for lights on the right.
